    "descripcion": "3 ESSENTIAL (simple) questions for new leaders / managers. \n\n1. What is expected of me in this role and what mandate do I have?\n\n2. Who in my team is going to be with me long term, and who is not going to make it. \n\n3. What are we aiming to grow into as a team (values, growth, team success, people development, progression)? \n\nAnswer these and you’re a chance of success. \n\n#leaderbilt #leadership #management #newmanager #christiancunningham @Let’s Just Start Podcast ",
